<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Photography Subdomains</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #8e44ad; /* Purple for creativity/art */
        }

        .subdomain {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .subdomain h3 {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #9b59b6; /* Lighter purple */
        }

        .subdomain p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .demand, .colleges, .scholarships {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Photography Subdomains</h1>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Portrait Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Focuses on capturing the personality and essence of individuals or groups, often used for personal or professional purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Fashion Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Involves photographing clothing and accessories for magazines, catalogs, and advertising campaigns, emphasizing style and aesthetics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Wildlife Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Focuses on capturing animals in their natural habitats, requiring patience, skill, and knowledge of wildlife behavior.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Landscape Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Involves capturing the beauty of natural environments, emphasizing composition, light, and atmosphere.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Product Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Focuses on photographing products for commercial purposes, highlighting their features and details for marketing and advertising.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Event Photography</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Involves capturing moments and scenes at events such as weddings, concerts, and corporate gatherings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="subdomain">
            <h2>Photojournalism</h2>
            <h3>Description:</h3>
            <p>Focuses on capturing news and documentary images, telling stories through powerful visuals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="demand">
            <h2>Demand for Photographers</h2>
            <p>The demand for photographers is driven by:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The growth of digital media and online content.</li>
                <li>The increasing importance of visual content in marketing and advertising.</li>
                <li>The demand for high-quality images in e-commerce and product promotion.</li>
                <li>The need for professional photographers in event coverage and personal photography.</li>
                <li>The rise of social media and the demand for visually appealing content.</li>
                <li>The growth of the film and television industry.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="colleges">
            <h2>Colleges for Photography Courses in India</h2>
            <p>Some prominent institutions offering photography courses include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad</li>
                <li>Light & Life Academy, Ooty</li>
                <li>Mass Communication Research Centre, Jamia Millia Islamia, New Delhi</li>
                <li>Asian Academy of Film and Television (AAFT), Noida</li>
                <li>Sir J.J. School of Art, Mumbai</li>
                <li>Delhi College of Photography (DCP), New Delhi</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="scholarships">
            <h2>Scholarships for Photography Courses</h2>
            <p>Scholarships and financial aid options may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Merit-based scholarships from universities and colleges.</li>
                <li>Need-based scholarships for students with financial constraints.</li>
                <li>Industry-sponsored scholarships from photography studios and companies.</li>
                <li>Government scholarships for arts and media studies.</li>
                <li>Scholarships from private organizations supporting photography education.</li>
                <li>Specific scholarships offered by institutions for photography students.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Always verify scholarship details with the respective institutions or government websites.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>